ink for more info.<BR> <A HREF="http://www.geocities.com/lordhong/sky.htm" TARGET=_blank>http://www.geocities.com/lordhong/sky.htm</A> <P>Caelym<BR>Templar of Tunare<BR>Zhaaz<BR>Disciple of Cazic Thule</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#f7f7f7"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Geneze</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">cool, thanks for infos....gonna be a looong weekend  <IMG SRC="http://eqcleric.gameglow.com/ubb/tongue.gif"></FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#dedfdf"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Gniss Fleshmender</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Always see 2 or three drop on the horse isle.... can't remember if that's 4 or 5 though.<P>------------------<BR>The Drunkard of Domus Divanae<BR>Prexus</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#f7f7f7"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Panteroo</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">I just got my WoTG's off of the boss mob on Isle 3 about 15 min ago</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#dedfdf"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Josiefuz</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">I've seen it drop from a normal key-fairy on isle 1.  Definately a random drop.<P>-Fuz<BR></FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#f7f7f7"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Gorian</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">heh....got mine on i5  just as we were bout to leave after geting 4 warrior blades =)</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#dedfdf"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Panteroo</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Your warriors must be happy !<P>We farmed 11 spiroc lords and not a single blade dropped at all  <IMG SRC="http://eqcleric.gameglow.com/ubb/frown.gif"><P><P>------------------<BR>Panteroo Mcgillakudy<BR>Patriarch of the Patron Saints<BR>Fennin Ro</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#f7f7f7"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Vamenea</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE=